      "Text": "Security update for cpp-httplib",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for cpp-httplib fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2025-53629: header can allocate memory arbitrarily in the server, potentially leading to its exhaustion\n  (bsc#1246471).\n- CVE-2025-53628: HTTP header smuggling due to insecure trailers merge (bsc#1246468).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
